{"tid":1117344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇緊 space X 直播","createTime":"2019-04-20T15:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T16:22:12.000Z","uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9381e059695cfe28b74b84599857693b047a6f7","tid":1117344,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DPfHHls50-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDPfHHls50-w&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=6c2f6410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DPfHHls50-w</a><br />\n<br />\n兩分鐘後發射 falcon heavy"},{"pid":"eacf3df6fb884217d3542bfecf583c4ddba70295","tid":1117344,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"屌，原來重播黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睽違一年，SpaceX 的重型火箭 Falcon Heavy 終於再次一展身手，在今天稍早完成了商用衛星 Arabsat-6A 的發射任務。一如去年的試飛，我們又再次欣賞到了兩支助推火箭同時著陸的英姿，這次中央的核心也順利著陸在海上等待的平台上了。<br />\n<br />\n去年的 Falcon Heavy 試飛時，美中不足的是中央的核心未能著陸。在點火液體耗盡後，中央的核心在最後階段無法啟動減速，因此火箭一頭栽在了平台旁的海中。不過，由於試飛的 Falcon Heavy 都是使用舊版的火箭，本來再次利用的機會也不大（SpaceX 去年一直在把舊火箭拋棄，挪出空間來給新的 Block 5 版本使用），因此一般都認為第二支 Falcon Heavy 火箭要等到 Falcon 9 Block 5 有了一定的實測基礎，且累積一定數量後，才能分配三支供 Falcon Heavy 使用。<br />\n<br />\n這一等，就是一年多的時間，才終於又迎來了一次 Falcon Heavy 的發射。據 Musk 的說法，在升級成 Block 5 規格之後，Falcon Heavy 的推力又再增加了 10%，而且重複使用力又有了很大的提升。不過有點意外的是，被送上地球同步轉移軌道的 Arabsat-6A 衛星雖然有 6,000 多公斤，算得上是「重量級」的衛星，但其實小支的 Falcon 9 Block 5 就曾在去年七月發射了重達 7,076 公斤的 Telstar 19V 到達一樣的軌道，而且之後還順利回收，可見用 Falcon Heavy 來發射 Arabsat-6A 是殺雞用牛刀的。不過當初簽約的時候，Falcon 9 還沒有發展到現今的程度，當時只有 Falcon Heavy 才能勝任，而且 Falcon Heavy 可以將衛星送到更高的軌道，讓衛星早點開始賺錢，所以就出現這種奇怪的現象囉。<br />\n<br />\n在這次的\b任務後，下一個 Falcon Heavy 出場的機會是美國空軍的 STP-2 任務，預計夏天進行。STP-2 本身是發射一大堆的實驗用和軍用小衛星上太空，但更重要的，美國空軍要為 Falcon Heavy 執行軍方任務進行評估 與認證，一切順利的話，未來美國空軍或許會是 Falcon Heavy 最大的客戶之一呢。"},{"pid":"41a1d7652567ed4ccf043d744cdf18b05843f3bf","tid":1117344,"uid":1876,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/d35/0e4/d350e4aa77d49f30c5b55d6bb38ecefcd00bcd19_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fd35%2F0e4%2Fd350e4aa77d49f30c5b55d6bb38ecefcd00bcd19_b.jpg&h=de8f2400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75d3e2fb35b2de301231fc1c9eb51f4bc7c345e3","tid":1117344,"uid":34174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"尋日都有重播，已經柒左次，你廿四個鐘後再柒"},{"pid":"5b099c3f5f818c5273c3f4aa587a1ee256e00439","tid":1117344,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75d3e2fb35b2de301231fc1c9eb51f4bc7c345e3","tid":1117344,"uid":34174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"尋日都有重播，已經柒左次，你廿四個鐘後再柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"第一次睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc1a70ce0f448613680002b5e6e64dc6e980fd8","tid":1117344,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"今日先有個post中左伏<br />\n而家又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到spacex直播但唔係spacex官方channel而係寫著&quot;SPACE &amp; UNIVERSE (Official)&quot;就係content farm假channel"},{"pid":"b58d7a8cd5dc61169a4c8b377f86f20bf0230f3f","tid":1117344,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d3e2fb35b2de301231fc1c9eb51f4bc7c345e3","tid":1117344,"uid":34174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"尋日都有重播，已經柒左次，你廿四個鐘後再柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"佢係第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab28dc78b8477d0a25b2895b5b9d954ccb29f7e","tid":1117344,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"呢個post 係第幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"